12:23:37.000Z","msg":"SIP唔係SPI 書包咩<br />\nFull rank升職只係跳point<br />\n唔係一下去到7雞<br />\n同埋消防一樣full rank快升<br />\n有人唔做走去做狗？"},{"pid":"d701225cd56d534848fc7a44bf272dc710230023","tid":2016481,"uid":39215,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T12:33:07.000Z","msg":"俾全世界杯先得個五萬蚊<br />\nU grad係醒既遲早都搵到<br />\n自己諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4115682d6865331e408176d23f99511927d2455","tid":2016481,"uid":22234,"like":27,"dislike":2,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T12:33:21.000Z","msg":"有人唔做走去做狗<br />\n<br />\n見到份糧就心郁<br />\n<br />\n睇你都係廢物黎 成唔到大事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"433f4b0e1400d15a14635f74e64857d867103699","tid":2016481,"uid":128895,"like":110,"dislike":6,"score":104,"quote":{"pid":"e8a1289ca1629fa71809f6094bc21af6ee58474f","tid":2016481,"uid":152224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T11:52:25.000Z","msg":"1. 人工高 ($47690)，升職快 (5年考筆試升SPI $76095，其他部隊要10年)<br />\n2. 大量福利、津貼，好快排到宿舍<br />\n3. 其他部隊officer爭崩頭 (入境、海關、懲教、救護 100爭1，警察20爭1)<br />\n4. 有炮有權有勢有地位 <br />\n<br />\np.s. hku grad 想考入境、海關，但太多人爭 ，冇信心考到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屋企人想我考PI，而家好易入"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T12:40:37.000Z","msg":"我都想考，樓豬一齊努力？<br />\n<br />\nSo far我淨係諗到呢幾個原因<br />\n我諗應該都outstand到<br />\n<br />\n1. 自己嘅problem solving 思維同警察嘅相似<br />\n我由細到大都好鍾意解決難嘅問題，挑戰自己<br />\n遇到難嘅問題通常就打9條友，解決唔到就強姦佢，或者屈佢。相信自己嘅personalities係警察所需嘅。<br />\n<br />\n2. 唔鍾意畀人管，鍾意打橫嚟，做警察可以滿足到我呢啲要求<br />\n由細到大都唔鍾意守法律，細細個畀老師話，我都直接會用胡椒噴霧噴9佢哋，但係始終佢擺上法庭告我，就冇佢符。如果我做咗警察之後，我做乜7都得，成個政府都係我嘅人。<br />\n<br />\nps: ive grad<br />\n<br />\n樓豬hku grad未必入到，聽講非ive唔請，驚洗唔到腦。"},{"pid":"f2bfed711d57a207c89210fd79c43b63c98cfd17","tid":2016481,"uid":18547,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T12:52:36.000Z","msg":"識有人真係為左「權」走去做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4d58e929acc3187d8b0768f5ec45c40302e1f48","tid":2016481,"uid":1161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T13:02:55.000Z","msg":"你係連登問係咪搏屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2e775fc33a0870249a24c14a41b7000f6878c37","tid":2016481,"uid":213959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T13:06:13.000Z","msg":"建議販毒 黑警都做緊 考都唔使考"},{"pid":"ce21280242b21d905563b87317e7d867de3ec824","tid":2016481,"uid":303702,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T13:28:55.000Z","msg":"你咁樣問我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔通同你講：支持樓主，黃竹炕見咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n樓主你真係要做嘅就唔好理咩人權咩自由啦，安安分分做個政權需要嘅警察等2047喇<br />\n<br />\n預備好被人屌老母未？伯母ready就去考喇<br />\n預備好一齊販毒未？心態ready就去馬喇<br />\n預備好被人話你強姦犯未？細佬ready就去馬喇<br />\n其實唔介意被人杯被人屌嘅話真係無咩所謂<br />\n最多得閒就上老豆搵仔睇下有無自己名嘅啫<br />\n<br />\n無事嘅<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />將來一定係學堂再見嘅，到時再俾禮你sir !"},{"pid":"8a320abe35ca36749b6038cdbe0561540fb29085","tid":2016481,"uid":303702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T13:32:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />push"},{"pid":"19db6a9a13ba25121d0cd86c81398f1d9534645c","tid":2016481,"uid":303702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T13:32:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />push"},{"pid":"9b01012aef3cf2713287c17b1a25481b0be03bba","tid":2016481,"uid":4179,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"624b55a3a621caa52b0606fd0aade9b90a93da68","tid":2016481,"uid":152224,"like":1,"dislike":28,"score":-27,"quote":{"pid":"e5d1722ae82655bcccc500c2d21c39edc4603856","tid":2016481,"uid":66059,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2